{
  "stem": "1753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 134.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I heard it-- I heard the shooting all day and all night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then it got quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] About-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and by the way, the shed that I was in was covered.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then it got dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then I heard airplanes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Then I heard the rain fall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was raining.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the lights start surrounded the camp were turned off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then there was-- then the Allied planes-- I don't know if they were Russians or whether from the Western forces-- they dropped a parachute flare that illuminated the entire area like it's daytime.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Only one flare, and I could see it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] About half an hour it would drop and that was the end.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It got very quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Then afterwards, I started to get-- I thought I'd make my way out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And as I tried, some of the lumbar shifted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Seconds later, two guards looked and came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Couldn't find me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I crawled back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I said to myself, now-- I said to myself, as I was sitting there, and I heard many, many others make the same-- many survivors, make the same statement.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I said to myself, I believe I'm the only Jew in all Europe alive, I said to myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I heard that comment many times before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously, it wasn't so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, how am I going to get out of this camp?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After all, you've got one barbed wire section, then there's two yards in between.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's another barbed wire section.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
